"list. Note, that the captcha point <em>default challenge</em> will be "
"used as the challenge type for the created CAPTCHA challenges."
msgstr ""
"Adiciona CAPTCHA a todos os formulários do Drupal, independentemente "
"da lista de Pontos de Captcha. Observe que o ponto de captcha "
